{"word":"ἀλάβαστρον","slug":"ἀλάβαστρον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀλάβαστρον</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀλάβαστος'><el>ἀλάβαστος</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>Prob. a foreign word.\n<p/><i>a box</i> or <i>casket of alabaster</i>, in <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b>, <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <el>ἀλάβαστρα ορ</el> <el>-τα</el> in <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b> and <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/>"}]}